-library surface.\",\"HarmonyOS Cangjie docs include album-specific API references such as `class_Album.md`, confirming the target platform has a real album-discovery path if a later source phase needs it.\"],\"discoveryOnlyEvidence\":[],\"compileProbeEvidence\":[],\"preResolutionDecision\":\"resolved-not-applicable\",\"phaseCapabilityResolution\":\"resolved-not-applicable\",\"blocker\":\"\",\"targetFallback\":\"\",\"futureCompletionPath\":\"\",\"notes\":\"The phase capability was over-detected from generic `gallery` term matches in source/resource data. Phase-04 home/history behavior uses packaged assets and repository-backed selection/filter flows only; closing this row as not-applicable keeps the real HarmonyOS media API recorded without widening current-phase scope.\",\"capabilityFacts\":{\"schemaVersion\":1,\"resolutionKind\":\"not-applicable\",\"activeFallback\":{\"used\":false,\"fallbackKind\":\"\",\"reason\":\"\",\"blocker\":\"\"},\"apiEvidence\":[{\"kind\":\"cangjie-sdk-declaration\",\"detail\":\"`ohos.file.photo_access_helper` is declared in the current Cangjie SDK, including `getPhotoAccessHelper(...)` and `PhotoAccessHelper.getAlbums(...)`, proving a direct target media-library API exists if later phases require it.\"},{\"kind\":\"cangjie-callable-api\",\"detail\":\"HarmonyOS Cangjie MediaLibraryKit docs document `PhotoAccessHelper`, `Album`, and related media APIs as callable Cangjie interfaces.\"}],\"discoveryOnlyEvidence\":[],\"compileProbeEvidence\":[],\"targetEndpoints\":[],\"blocker\":{\"used\":false,\"kind\":\"\",\"detail\":\"\",\"futureCompletionPath\":\"\"},\"factsSource\":\"agent\"}}]}' }","description":"Patch media capability authority entry","timeout":120000,"workdir":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike"},"output":"patch-authority: Could not read patch payload: [Errno 22] Invalid argument: 'D:\\\\workspace\\\\Foodike\\\\{updates:[{capabilityId:media-library-access,status:not-applicable,plannedPhase:phase-04-home-history,targetCapabilitySearch:[Phase-04 s